PRESS ANY KEY

ANIMUS: He wants to hit you.

SINEW: Let him try. Lovers kiss and fuck on the battlefields of his youth. We could easily take this old man.

"ISAAC can not miss a dose. Not now," DESMOND says running his hands through his short graying hair. "We'll need to sythansize more here. I need a compound called essage. Head into town and find more. Start with starports and clinics. This city is ancient, they should have some in storage somewhere."

SYNAPSE: The starport is too new, you won't find any there. We saw a clinic on the way here though.

Bathroom >>> WEST
