NORTHERN LANE, CIVIC RESOURCE DISTRICT

You make your way through the dark into the northern lane of the CR District. Flame lamps glow in long flickering rows. Though the port is some distance away, you can hear the roar of ships as they flee the cold. You look up to see the pusling glows of green and red of their anti-collision lights refracting throughout the black clouds.

The steel tracks of a light rail STATION cut across the district's lane. Beyond, you see a long paved road that leads to the port, where you ship is waiting. There is a BAR nearby, its opaque windows lit with flickering amber light. An OFFICE stands out with its bright white exterior amongst the monochromatic world.

Port >>> NORTH
Bar >>> WEST
Office Building >>> EAST
