Notre Feu

No one but the BARTENDER seems to notice your presence as you pass through the doorway. He knows everyone on Bluèl and he does not know you. Immediatly, he sets down the beer he was filling up, resting his massive hands on his hips. The patron looks at his half-empty pint, dejected, but takes it and walks away silently.

 ANIMUS: The barman's freeing up his hands in case he needs them. In case, you do something stupid.

 SINEW: Violence. That's the stupid thing he's waiting for you to do.

You feel the PISTOL beneath your coat as you raise both hands as a sign of peace. With a nod, the BARTENDER gives you permission to enter his domain.

 As the morning progresses, several drinkers have switched to coffee before heading out to their jobsites. Although you spot plenty who are attempting to get one more drink into their bloodstreams, including two WORKERS deep in conversation.

DESMOND  sits alone at a table just near the entrance.  "Don't bother. This is a company bar so they only take tokens. They won't even let me buy a beer with cash."

SHANTI, the worker from the GasTechnin offices, is at the bar arguing with the BARTENDER. Their eyes and voice are steady as they speak, both hands pressing firmly against the wooden bartop.

PRESS ANY KEY

“Yes, I know they are drink tokens, but I just want some rice. You sell that here, no?,” they say.

“For the last time, they are only good for drinks,” the BARTENDER replies tersely before looking closer at the tokens in their hands. “And only beer”

“What about the bathroom? It is always disgusting. I can clean it.”

“Bathroom’s fines. Now order something or get out.”

The bartender walks away to the other end of the bar, where a queue has started to grow. A rapid stream of swears follow him in a foreign language.

PRESS ANY KEY

SYNAPSE: Some dialect from Capricorn perhaps? I can’t be sure.

 ANIMUS: They called him an asshole. We don’t need a translator to know that.

SHANTI collapses into a seat at a table crammed in the corner, fiddling with their unused drink tokens.

