You walk through the streets of the CR District with a sense of relief. It's been so long the feeling is almost foreign. Julia's repairs almost complete and you are one step closer to getting off this depressing planet. That's when you see him, marching joyously across the street towards you: the GasTechnin SECRETARY.

"Hello, sir, hello!," he shouts before is even close to you.

SINEW: Not him again. I might have to rough him up a bit before this is all over.

