"Okay, well, then it's settled. You can visit me at the office as soon as possible and we'll get you all sorted. Paperwork, fitted for your uniform, a training video or two. See you soon!"

You watch him proudly walk away and head into GasTechnin's offices.

ISAAC looks up at you.

"Set us free
Even if a blood sacrifice is demanded.
Surst is waiting."

