GasTechnin Offices

The POSTERs and LOGOs plastered across the well-lit office tell you that this is GasTechnin's main office for Bluèl. A SECRETARY for the company sits smiling broadly behind a desk, typing at a electronic terminal. There are rows of desk behind him behind, but all remain blank and unstaffed.

The entire space is bright and free of the perennial grime that seems to coat the rest of the city. Unlike the other buildings you've seen, this space is lit with electric lightbulbs. Emerald green plants of plastic decorate each of the four corners. You nearly forget what planet you're on.

The SECRETARY smiles wide. He's waiving a thick stack of papers in the air.

SYNAPSE: It's an employment contract.

ANIMUS: He actually thinks you're going to sign it.

"Alright, how exciting. Are you ready to get to work?"

CR Disitrict >>> WEST
